      <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col lg:justify-center">
        <div class="py-5 pb-0 container xl:text-center">
          <h1 class="text-7xl font-bold mb-8">
            A Talent Manager for Every Creator
          </h1>
          <p class="text-3xl mb-4 text-slate-200">
            Repbot does 80% of what a talent manager does - without taking a 20%
            commission on your brand deals.
          </p>
          <p class="text-3xl text-slate-200">
            We qualify your inbound leads, negotiate better rates, and help you
            spend more time on the creative part of being a creator.
            <u>All for free</u>.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="py-10 container xl:flex xl:flex-col xl:items-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl uppercase font-bold mb-4">ðŸ‘‡ Join The Waitlist</h3>
          <WaitlistForm client:load />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container mb-5 font-bold text-slate-300">
        We exist to help you...
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container py-6 flex flex-col justify-center mb-12 mt-2">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
        ðŸ‘‹ Say Goodbye to Sh*t Affiliate Deals from Russian Mobile Game
        Spammers.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl leading-8 text-slate-200">
        Repbot asks brands for the important deal details <i>upfront</i>. This
        enables you to filter out the noise before it ever reaches your inbox.
        No more wasting time scouring the internet trying to see if a company or
        product is legit. And if you never want to see another affiliate deal in
        your life, now you don't have to.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="container py-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
        ðŸ’ª Maximize Your Sponsorship Revenue with a Ruthless, Informed
