        that takes into account your minimum rate, social metrics, and data from
        past deals across all creators using Repbot. However, brands are still
        in control of their offer at the end of the day - our goal in
        negotiation is simply to advocate for fair pay.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="container py-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
        ðŸ‘€ Compare Deals at a Glance. Accept the Best Fit. And Get Back to Work.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl leading-8 text-slate-200">
        Repbot give you an easy way to read and review your inbound brand deals.
        When one catches your eye, all you have to do is hit "Reply". Then, we
        get out of the way and let you handle communication, contracting,
        invoicing and payment with the tools you already use to run your
        business.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="container py-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
        ðŸ”¥ Fire Us Whenever. We're Free Forever.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl leading-8 text-slate-200">
        Repbot exists so that you never have to sign with a manager that will
        take 15% of your business in exchange for barely managing your email
        inbox. But if better representation comes along, we want you to take it.
        No fees. No contractural obligations or early exist clauses. We see
        ourselves as a stepping stone to an agency that will help you with
        outbound, hiring, and product development if that's the route you choose
        to go with your business.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
</style>
